org.sql: SELECT relations.* FROM relations WHERE relations.to_id IS NULL AND relations.hierarchy = "$1" AND relations.relates = "$2" AND relations.duplicates = "$3" AND relations.follows = "$4" AND relations.blocks = "$5" AND relations.includes = "$6" AND relations.requires = "$7" LIMIT "$8"

rewrites.sql: SELECT relations.* FROM relations WHERE False AND relations.hierarchy = "$1" AND relations.relates = "$2" AND relations.duplicates = "$3" AND relations.follows = "$4" AND relations.blocks = "$5" AND relations.includes = "$6" AND relations.requires = "$7" LIMIT "$8"
